                            <p>Each cat has it's own personality. If you find your cat acting out of the ordanary, think
                                about
                                making
                                a vet appointment to make sure everyhing is ok. Always make necessary vet appointments
                                if
                                needed.
                                Also important to note: when cats feel sick they tend to hide away. If you have other
                                pets that
                                don't get along
                                with your new cat, either spend the necessary time and effort to sociallize them better.
                                If that
                                doesn't work then
                                maybe this cat was not the right fit.
                            </p>
